Package: DataTransformation
Type: Package
Title: Advanced Data Transformation and Aggregation for Regression Modeling
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Zainab Said Alhosni<[s133464@student.squ.edu.om]>
Maintainer: Zainab Said Al Hosni <s133464@student.squ.edu.om>
Description: Implements advanced data transformation methods (e.g., logarithmic, Box-Cox, Z-score, Min-Max Normalization) and aggregation techniques (e.g., summing, averaging, weighted aggregation, moving averages). Includes tools for regression modeling with transformed data.
